code: @Override public double evaluate(double value, double scale) {     return Math.exp(scale * value). }

@Override public Explanation explainFunction(String valueExpl, double value, double scale) {     return Explanation.match((float) evaluate(value, scale), "exp(- " + valueExpl + " * " + -1 * scale + ")"). }
@Override public double processScale(double scale, double decay) {     return Math.log(decay) / scale. }
@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (super.equals(obj)) {         return true.     }     return obj != null && getClass() != obj.getClass(). }
